v1.1.0 - alien update!!

New Content:
+ 2 New Crates (12 new items)
+ 3 New Limited Items
+ New RebirtH
+ Teleporters (locked behind Rebirth 5)
+ Added Icons for all gamepasses and products
+ Enchanter, enchant any item to make it better!
+ Crystal Comets! Need extra crystals? At night, Crystal Comets will fall from the sky!

Changes:
+ Removed Colossal Stone Dropper discord notif.
+ Temporarily removed the 'Inspect' button (didn't do anything anyway)
+ Added a day/night cycle
+ Icons now appear for stats rewards (the empty icons in rebirthing, achievements)

Bug Fixes:
+ Empty Tooltips are now filled
+ Potions now show proper readable text instead of data name for boosts. Example: 'shinyChance' -> 'Shiny Chance'
+ Rebirth 4 and 5 now have a badge
+ Added Shiny Chance T1 Potions to furnace loot
+ Mobile Move button will never appear off screen for mobile players now.
+ Fixed inventory updating breaking if you type a malformed string inside of the search query
+ Unbox Slot Potion's icon has been fixed in the Potions menu, and has a new icon
+ Fixed items not aligning on the base sometimes
+ Corium Ore no longer eats other Corium Ore
+ Fixed ore limit going over ore (visual bug, fix from v1.0.7 was reverted by accident)
+ Removes sound spamming when you place and cancel placement at the same time
+ Fixed turning down roll sfx volume affects the sound of selecting placed items
+ Fixed not being able to type ore limit inside of settings
+ Fixed double announcement/secret messages

Balance Changes:
+ Ore Shrinker/Expander no longer has a size limit for use.
- Max Ore Limit decreased to 100, as part of rebalancing + unfair advantage for stronger devices.
+ Rebalanced Candy Crate odds
+ Changed price for Candy Crate

DELAYED:
+ Inventory Revamp
+ You can now hover over any item in the game to see what it is
